a:50:{i:1331631;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331631";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:370:"The guards huff and retrain their lances on StarlightWing. &quot;Then no more funny business&quot; the one who&#039;d held onto his lance properly says. &quot;We&#039;re not afraid of you and neither is Princess Sapphire.&quot; They move to flanking position and begin marching her down the hallway. &quot;She&#039;s in the throne room, but I guess you knew that.&quot; ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429920024";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299200271";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331633;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331633";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"84";s:6:"handle";s:13:"StarlightWing";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"182";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:491:"/me headed with them with a roll of here eyes.. &quot; You shouldn&#039;t be... I&#039;m not your enemy...&quot; she smiles at them both alittle. &quot; Monsters are not all evil but many are wicked and have a reason to exist... Forecample there must always be balance light and dark good and evil... You have all lived a long time have you not? Lived and died only to live again... Honestly... I wonder what it&#039;s like to feel that... Maybe I will find out by the end of tonight..&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429920602";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#65287b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299206016";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#196f70";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331635;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331635";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:439:"The two guards look at each other uncertainly, but say nothing. Instead they lead StarlightWing to the throne room. Sapphire Night was, rather uncharacteristically, sitting in her chair properly with a pair of guards flanking the usually unprotected steps which led up to it. &quot;Your highness!&quot; One of the guards with Starlight calls as they enter the chamber. &quot;We found her sneaking around near her sisters&#039; room.&quot; ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429922447";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299224476";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331637;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331637";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"84";s:6:"handle";s:13:"StarlightWing";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"182";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:159:"/me smiles up at Sapphire. &quot; Hello your Highness... I wonder if you were expecting me to show up on your door step... Or perhaps you plan all this..&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429922683";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#65287b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299226828";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#196f70";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331638;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331638";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:282:"&quot;After you left Ponyville last night, I had a fairly good idea that you&#039;d come back here&quot; she replies. The guards remain totally still at the base of her platform, and the others cover the door. &quot;So while I wasn&#039;t -expecting- it, I was hoping for it.&quot; ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429922860";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299228607";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331640;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331640";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"84";s:6:"handle";s:13:"StarlightWing";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"182";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:335:"/me Smart pony, butwhat will you do now that you have me here now Princess? Rip what saved my life away from me? Lock me away? Or do you plan to have me join the towns folk as a gholst myself? I wonder.... What your plans are.... Or will step down ... no you have made up your mind on that... So...perhaps there is another way...&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429923124";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#65287b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299231239";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#196f70";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331641;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331641";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:397:"&quot;You&#039;re confused about quite a lot...but you&#039;re right about one. I won&#039;t step down for you. Not like this.&quot; Her voice echos about the room a little as she remains calmly seated, the only other sound coming from the twin waterfalls on either side of the throne. &quot;As for you...if you can&#039;t use the Darkness responsibly, I think you should get rid of it, yes.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429923273";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299232738";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331647;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331647";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"84";s:6:"handle";s:13:"StarlightWing";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"182";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:1008:"/me lowers her ears. &quot; Tell me what a creature of the darness is supposed to do responsibly with it&#039;s power then Princess.... I do have a sujestion how ever... A old mare told me is she lost to someone even if she was better fo the job... THat she woudl still help them... Aid them request to advise them... We have not nobles in this contry no lords no ladies... You have friends... Few an far between Princess.. I can not ever be apony of light... I&#039;ll never give up the gift I was given... Not my dream.... But maybe I can... Try to obtain it another way... For now.. I have hurt ponies.. I have hurt my friends... Ponies I do not deserve to even look in the eyes anymore... So then Punish me Princess.... Or I will leave here and follow my fist path... I do not know what is better power or modesty... But I know I can not survives destroying my friens so instead I will destroy myself if you make me walk out that door Princess. Please.. as my friend, and my princess... Make yoru choice.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429923978";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#65287b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299239776";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#196f70";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331652;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331652";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:1168:"Sapphire sits silently for a moment, staring down at StarlightWing. &quot;That&#039;s your problem, Starlight. Not everything is so black and white&quot; she replies softly. &quot;Giving up your Darkness doesn&#039;t mean giving up on your dream...and if I choose not to punish you, that doesn&#039;t mean you&#039;re free to continue trying to overthrow parts of Equestria. It certainly doesn&#039;t mean you HAVE to.&quot; She stands up from her seat and trots to the edge of the platform the throne stood on. &quot;As long as I&#039;ve known you, you seem to think you&#039;re not good enough. That you&#039;re in competition with somepony... I can understand that, really, but you&#039;ll never prove yourself better than someone else.&quot; She puts a hoof to her chest. &quot;I myself spent almost my whole life in my sisters&#039; shadow...and when I finally got out I fell into the shadow of the Princesses. And all the time I chased this unattainable goal of being just AS GOOD as they were, I was never happy. It wasn&#039;t until I began to follow my own path again that I succeeded. I know it&#039;s not easy, but it is what&#039;s right, Starlight.&quot; ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429925608";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299256080";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331653;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331653";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"84";s:6:"handle";s:13:"StarlightWing";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"182";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:736:"/me sighs softly stepping towards Sapphire then sat beside her.. &quot; Then... I will ask you again... Since i can not take it give me the chance to try and help it along side you... As your friend... As your familey... You are ever part as much my family as Ashley is .. You have watched me grow into a mare.. But I can not give up my powers... They saved me.. they stilll do I am asking you to help me use them for something... I love this city every ounce as much as you do... I love the poeple here... living and unliving alike... But you can not simply forgive me.. for attacking you.. for trying to hurt you or for what i did to Seabreeze... All i cna think to do is help ponies that was all i ever wanted... Was to love them... ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429926055";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#65287b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299260542";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#196f70";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331654;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331654";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:607:"&quot;I can and do forgive you for attacking me&quot; she replies simply, sitting down next to Starlight. &quot;Because I have had that power you have now...and I know what it&#039;s doing to you, even if you won&#039;t admit it.&quot; She rolls her eyes over the smaller mare, just staring at her somewhat sadly. &quot;I think deep inside yourself, you do love this town and these ponies...but you have not acted in a way that reflects that. You acted selfishly to gain something for yourself...not for them. But there is something I will give you, and only if you promise to take it very seriously.&quot; ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429926604";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299266043";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331655;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331655";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"84";s:6:"handle";s:13:"StarlightWing";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"182";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:305:"/me nods her head slowly.&quot; You are right... I did... I was envyous of you... My sister too.. Your both strong ponies... I am strong tooo but not like you... I will do what ever it takes Sapphire I won&#039;t give up on my dream... but I can not use my power to obtain it... I realize that now..&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429926784";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#65287b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299267843";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#196f70";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331659;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331659";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"84";s:6:"handle";s:13:"StarlightWing";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"182";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:211:"/me moved her shadows around the princess but they harbored no ill intent. Starlight smiled alittle. &quot; I am not sure where my road will lead.. But... I am ready to head down it... I am scared though..&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429927400";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#65287b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299274000";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#196f70";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331660;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331660";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:580:"&quot;It&#039;s okay to be scared when starting down a new road...you just have to have faith in yourself. That&#039;s all you can ever really do&quot; she says, nodding. &quot;Now, what I am going to give you, Starlight...is a second chance. I&#039;ll see if we can get you in as an aide to the Mayor in town...and from there, you&#039;re free to work towards whatever you like. But if I find out you&#039;re misusing your Darkness, I&#039;ll take it away. I can&#039;t allow you to hurt anypony&quot; she says. &quot;And there&#039;s something else you need to do for me.&quot; ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429927572";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299275726";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331661;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331661";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"84";s:6:"handle";s:13:"StarlightWing";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"182";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:132:"/me &quot; I don&#039;t know anything about being an aid... But I will do my best.... What else do you need me to do Princess?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429927661";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#65287b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299276607";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#196f70";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331664;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331664";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:650:"&quot;You don&#039;t know anything about being a Princess, and that almost didn&#039;t stop you&quot; she says, smiling a little bit at Starlight. &quot;You&#039;ll &lt;i&gt;learn&lt;/i&gt;. And that&#039;s the whole point, Starlight. You&#039;ll learn and grow and develop...and when you&#039;re ready, you&#039;ll advance. Just like me and your sister and everypony else. And I know that you&#039;ll do great at it, if you really try your best. As for what I want you to do...&quot; she holds up her hoof and passes it right through Starlight&#039;s shadow-horn, causing it to waver a little. &quot;Get rid of this. It doesn&#039;t suit you.&quot; ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429927975";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299279755";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331669;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331669";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"84";s:6:"handle";s:13:"StarlightWing";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"182";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:378:"/me looks at the horn. &quot; I agree It&#039;s my focal point helps me use my magic better I din&#039;t know what else to make it into.. She looked down at the necklace she had made fo gold. &quot; Perhaps this is a better Idea... it&#039;s the first thing i have ever gotten from a friend... Oh umm who is the mayor in Bitter Springs anyway?&quot; She said her hoin vanishing.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429928248";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#65287b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299282476";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#196f70";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331676;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331676";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"84";s:6:"handle";s:13:"StarlightWing";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"182";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:9:"sapppy?))";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429929893";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#65287b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299298920";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#196f70";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331680;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331680";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:204:"&quot;it&#039;s not really a mayor, he&#039;s actually the town Elder. He lives down a few tiers in the clock-tower&quot; she says. &quot;I&#039;ll introduce you once we get this all settled, okay?&quot; ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429930571";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299305712";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331683;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331683";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"84";s:6:"handle";s:13:"StarlightWing";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"182";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:118:"/me nods her head a little. &quot; Alright... I willget my things.. and find someplace to say in the mean time..&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429931176";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#65287b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299311760";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#196f70";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331685;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331685";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:180:"&quot;I&#039;m not making you move out&quot; she replies. &quot;Although your sister might have something to say about that. She&#039;s not thrilled about the last few days.&quot; ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429931601";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299316018";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331686;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331686";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"84";s:6:"handle";s:13:"StarlightWing";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"182";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:133:"/me frowns a little.. &quot; I don&#039;t want to see her... I can not look her in the face... Have you seen her then recently?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429931667";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#65287b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299316671";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#196f70";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331689;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331689";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:150:"&quot;I&#039;ve met with her&quot; she replies, nodding. &quot;She&#039;s in training to be the head of my knights. She coordinates the others.&quot; ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429931876";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299318768";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331691;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331691";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"84";s:6:"handle";s:13:"StarlightWing";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"182";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:271:"/me &quot; I see... I will be moving my things... I will see my sister when I am ready to face her.. Right now I can not... If I am to stay here I will need my own room other wise I will move into town... And live on my own.. I am a mare now I can pprotect myself..&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429931994";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#65287b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299319937";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#196f70";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331695;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331695";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:224:"&quot;I think that&#039;s a very mature decision&quot; she says, nodding. &quot;And I know it&#039;ll work out 