xt_color";s:7:"#196f70";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331712;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331712";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:118:"/me nods. &quot;Well, then I&#039;ll leave you to it&quot; she says to Starlight, slowly getting to her hooves again. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429933546";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299335465";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331719;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331719";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"84";s:6:"handle";s:13:"StarlightWing";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"182";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:151:"/me remained sitting as she sank into the ground to vanish into the shadows into the roomm her form could be seen moving though them towards her room. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429933773";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#65287b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299337730";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#196f70";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331722;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331722";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:308:"Sapphire flops back into her throne and sighs heavily, rubbing her head a bit. The guards look at one another, waiting for orders. &quot;What...should we do, your highness?&quot; one of them asks. &quot;Keep an eye on her for now...but don&#039;t smother her. I said she&#039;d have her second chance.&quot; ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429934043";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299340436";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331723;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331723";s:12:"chat_