, Starlight is long gone. Either way, Sapphire remains where she is for the time being, more or less lost in thought. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429937538";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299375375";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331795;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331795";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"84";s:6:"handle";s:13:"StarlightWing";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"182";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:297:"/me peers out her window leaving the lantern on outside as she turned the on in the house off.. &quot;Not much but home is gonna be home I could never be home anyplace else...&quot; She unpacked her bags, settingbooks on a small shelf. as she curled up on the floor.. I&#039;m pretty tired..&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429938106";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#65287b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299381058";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#196f70";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331863;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331863";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Lonesome_Dove";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"75";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:360:"Outside StarlightWing&#039;s bedroom window she would see down below a single pony entering town along the highway. She was unaccompanied and moving with the speed of purpose. This was all perfectly normal for Lonesome_Dove. She must be here to visit SapphireNight. She had other friends here, but none quite so close. She was approachable, if usually distant.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429940884";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ff91f2";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299408672";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#abff9c";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331865;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331865";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"84";s:6:"handle";s:13:"StarlightWing";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"182";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:490:"/me watches from her window, the figure was hard to make out though the glass her eyes could not see them infact. Still she took a deep breath and stepped out of her home towards the pony. &quot;Greetings Miss, welcome to Bitter Springs! My naem is StarlightWing, I&#039;m the mayor&#039;s well soon to be the Mayor&#039;s aid. Pleased to meet you.. It is rather late is there somplace you perhaps need help finding? You are welcome to rest at my home or we can find you a lovely inn.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429941184";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#65287b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299411838";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#196f70";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331868;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331868";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Lonesome_Dove";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"75";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:136:"/me steps up to StarlightWing and pauses. After a moment, she answers simple, &quot;I have accomodations in the castle. Thank you.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429941279";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ff91f2";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299412624";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#abff9c";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331873;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331873";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"84";s:6:"handle";s:13:"StarlightWing";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"182";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:173:"/me looked at the mare for a long moment then nods... &quot; Wait... I know you... Your are mister Makabre&#039;s wife are you not?&quot; she asked trying to appear chipper.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429941478";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#65287b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299414780";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#196f70";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331877;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331877";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"19";s:7: